data.description: Meticulously cared for cape cod house in West Kettering! The front enclosed porch offers 4 season enjoyment of additional living space. Original knotty pine woodwork throughout. Living room has a brick wood burning fireplace with detailed woodwork mantle. Large kitchen with Z-brick wall, stylish backsplash, and newer cabinets with loads of space. Newer flooring throughout. Lots of natural light provided by sliding glass doors opening to the multi-level wood deck in the rear yard. Original clawfoot bathtub in bath. 2 bedrooms upstairs with much room for storage and a small south facing room ideal for reading or toys. Full unfinished open area basement with two additional rooms and a dedicated laundry area. Enclosed shower in basement. Fully fenced rear yard, nicely landscaped with walkway to large 2 car garage. Owner offering 1 year Home Warranty! Many updates including new water heater 2023, leaf guard gutters 2022 w/ transferrable warranty, newer windows 2018, water softener serviced 2023, McAfee furnace 2008. New gas lines and meter installed by City of Kettering 2023. Great location with close proximity to Hills & Dales Metro Park, Southern Hills Park, Carillon Historic Park, Miami Valley Bike Trails, Southdale Elementary & University of Dayton. This Is a must see!
